{{Infobox ancient site | name = Costești-Cetățuie Dacian fortress | native_name = '''Cetatea Dacica Costești-Cetățuie''' | native_name_lang =Romanian | alternate_name = | image = Cetatea Costesti.JPG | image_size = | alt = | caption = | map_type = Romania | map_alt = | map_caption = | map_size = | altitude_m = 514 | altitude_ref = | relief = Mountain Hilltop | coordinates = {{coord|45.680189|23.154285|display=inline,title}} | map_dot_label = | location = Cetățuie,&#8203;&nbsp;[[Costești]],&#8203;&nbsp;[[Hunedoara County|Hunedoara]],&#8203;&nbsp;[[Romania]] | area = Hunedoara County | built = Ist century BC | abandoned = 2nd century AD | epochs = <!-- actually displays as "Periods" --> | cultures = Dacian | event = [[Trajan's Dacian Wars]] | discovered = | excavations = | archaeologists = | condition = Ruined | designation1 = World Heritage Site | designation1_number = 906 | designation2 = Monument istoric | designation2_number = HD-I-s-A-03177 <ref name="lmi">{{cite web|title=National Register of Historic Monuments in Romania, Hunedoara County|url=http://www.inmi.ro/lmi/HUNEDOARA.pdf|publisher=www.inmi.ro|accessdate=18 October 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120227080850/http://www.inmi.ro/lmi/HUNEDOARA.pdf|archivedate=27 February 2012|df=}}</ref> | website = | architectural_styles = | architectural_details = | notes = }}
The '''Costești - Cetățuie''' dacian fortress was a [[Dacians|Dacian]] fortified town located in [[Hunedoara County|Hunedoara]], [[Romania]] and belongs to [[Dacian Fortresses of the Orăștie Mountains|The Six Dacian Fortresses]] in the Orăștie Mountains complex . The ancient fortress was built in the Ist century BC, during [[Burebista]]`s Rule with the purpose of defending against the [[Romans]]. It`s being found near the village of [[Costești]], [[Orăștioara de Sus]] comune. {{commons}}
==Information about the fortress== The site is located in the river valley of ''Apa Grădiștei''. The superior plateau of the hill where it`s situated is 514 m above the sea level. It was a strong fortress which had a defensive role. It`s being told that it had a civil settlement at the base and it was the regular residence of the Transylvanian dacian kings. Another important role was also the guarding of the road to [[Sarmizegetusa Regia]].
