{{Underlinked|date=March 2015}}
''''''Metro FM'''''' was established by ['''[Kathmandu Metropolitan City[[www.metrofm.org.np]]''']] . It received its operating license on March 9, 1998 from the government. After receiving the license, the station began its test transmission on September 17, 1998. On September 18, 1999, the station began its official transmission.
Originally, the station began its transmission on 106.7&nbsp;MHz. Currently, it is operating on 94.6&nbsp;MHz using 500 watts transmitter.
Currently, the station is on-air from 5:30 AM till 10 PM. The station is located in CITY HALL,Bhrikuti mandap, Kathmandu. This station can be listened online on http://www.metrofm.org.np
