{{Infobox diocese |jurisdiction = Diocese |name = Garissa |latin = Dioecesis Garissaënsis |local = Jimbo la Garissa |country = {{flag|Kenya}} |metropolitan = [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Mombasa|Mombasa]] |province = [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Mombasa|Mombasa]] |rite = [[Latin Rite]] |cathedral = Our Lady of Consolation Cathedral in [[Garissa]] |cocathedral = |area_km2 = 140,000 |population = 729,000 |population_as_of = 2006 |catholics = 6,690 |catholics_percent = 0.9 |pope = {{Incumbent pope}} |bishop = [[Joseph Alessandro]], [[O.F.M. Cap.]] |metro_archbishop = [[Martin Kivuva Musonde]] |coadjutor = |auxiliary_bishops = }}
The '''Roman Catholic Diocese of Garissa''' ({{lang-la|Garissaën(sis)}}) is a [[diocese]] located in the city of [[Garissa]]. It is administered under the [[Ecclesiastical province]] of [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Mombasa|Mombasa]] in [[Kenya]].
==History== * December 9, 1976: Established as Apostolic Prefecture of Garissa from the Diocese of Mombasa and [[Diocese of Meru]] * February 3, 1984: Promoted as Diocese of Garissa
==Leadership== * [[Bishop]]s of Garissa (Roman rite) ** Bishop [[Joseph Alessandro]], O.F.M. Cap. (2015.12.9 - Present) ** Bishop [[Paul Darmanin]], O.F.M. Cap. (February 3, 1984 - 2015.12.9) * Prefects Apostolic of Garissa (Roman rite) ** Fr. Leo White, O.F.M. Cap. (December 9, 1976 – 1984)
==See also== *[[Roman Catholicism in Kenya]]
==Sources== * [http://www.gcatholic.org/dioceses/diocese/gari0.htm GCatholic.org] * [http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dgari.html Catholic Hierarchy]
