'''Tshaneni Airfield''' {{airport codes||FDTS}} is an [[airstrip]] serving [[Tshaneni]], in [[Swaziland]].
The Sikhuphe [[VOR-DME]] (Ident: '''VSK''') is located {{convert|23.5|nmi|km|1}} south of Tshaneni. The Matsapha [[VOR-DME]] (Ident: '''SZ''') is located {{convert|32.4|nmi|km|1}} south-southeast of the airstrip.<ref>{{cite web |title=Sikhuphe VOR |url=https://skyvector.com/airport/FDTS/Tshanen-Airport |website=SkyVector |publisher=SkyVector Aeronautical Charts |accessdate=16 June 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ourairports.com/navaids/VMS/Matsapha_VOR-DME_SZ/|title=Matsapha VOR-DME (VMS) @ OurAirports|website=ourairports.com|access-date=2018-08-26}}</ref>
