{{Redirect-distinguish2|Golden Ring|the Dutch rock band [[Golden Earring]]}} {{Infobox musical artist <!-- See Wikipedia:WikiProject Musicians --> | name = Golden Ring | image = Nadieshda-p1040164.jpg | caption = | image_size = | background = group_or_band | alias = | origin = | genre = [[Contemporary folk music]] | years_active = 1988–present | label = | associated_acts = | website = [http://www.golden-ring.ru www.golden-ring.ru] | current_members = | past_members = }}
'''Golden Ring''' ({{lang-ru|Золотое кольцо}}, [[Romanization of Russian|transliteration]]: ''{{transl|ru|ALA|Zolotoye Koltso}}'') is a [[Russia]]n [[folk music]] group. It was founded in 1988 in [[Moscow]] by [[Nadezhda Kadysheva]] and her husband Alexander Kostyuk. The name of the group refers to the [[Golden Ring of Russia]].
==External links== * [http://www.golden-ring.ru Official webpage] * [https://web.archive.org/web/20071117020027/http://profile.myspace.com/index.cfm?fuseaction=user.viewprofile Official webpage on MySpace] * {{Discogs artist|Золотое Кольцо| Zolotoe Koltso}}
