'''Šarišan''' is Slovak folk music ensemble that was founded in 1967 in the town of [[Veľký Šariš]] (Great Šariš) from which the group's name derives. The ensemble currently is run by the ''Park kultúry a oddychu'' (The Center of Performing Arts) in [[Prešov]].

== Selected recordings ==
*''"Vitaj, život"'' (Welcome, life), videotape  
*''"Na Šarišu tak ..."'' (In Šariš it's so ...), DVD
*''"Na dachu ja"'' (On the roof), DVD

